ART: Visual art and craftsmanship

Category: Creative
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Producing and judging visual art: drawing, painting, sculpture, and
similar craft. Covers both making the work and recognizing when
someone else's is genuinely good.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, writing, singing, dancing
